column3: Forgive me, \x02\x08\x0f\xe9\x05\xff\x06madam\xff\x04sir\x03, but the House of Splendors does not accept unsolicited submissions. Pray speak with Lydirlona if you would like to become one of our suppliers.
A thousand pardons, \x02\x08\x0f\xe9\x05\xff\x06madam\xff\x04sir\x03, but we're still getting things in order. Come back later, eh?
